  <entry>
    <title>WSL + Docker Compose 一键部署 GeoServer + PostGIS</title>
    <link href="/2026/03/04/GeoServer/260304/"/>
    <url>/2026/03/04/GeoServer/260304/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="WSL-Docker-Compose-一键部署-GeoServer-PostGIS-完整教程"><a href="#WSL-Docker-Compose-一键部署-GeoServer-PostGIS-完整教程" class="headerlink" title="WSL + Docker Compose 一键部署 GeoServer + PostGIS 完整教程"></a>WSL + Docker Compose 一键部署 GeoServer + PostGIS 完整教程</h1><p>在 Windows 环境下做 GIS 开发，传统本地安装 GeoServer + PostGIS 步骤繁琐、环境冲突多、迁移麻烦。本文使用 <strong>WSL2 + Docker + Docker Compose</strong>，提供一套可直接复制使用的配置文件与脚本，实现<strong>一键启动、数据持久化、环境隔离</strong>，开发&#x2F;测试&#x2F;演示都非常稳定。</p><h2 id="一、环境说明"><a href="#一、环境说明" class="headerlink" title="一、环境说明"></a>一、环境说明</h2><ul><li>操作系统：Windows 10&#x2F;11（开启 WSL2）</li><li>容器工具：Docker Desktop（开启 WSL 集成）</li><li>镜像：<ul><li><code>kartoza/postgis:16-3.4</code>（PostgreSQL 16 + PostGIS 3.4）</li><li><code>kartoza/geoserver:2.25.0</code></li></ul></li><li>功能：<ul><li>PostGIS 空间数据库自动初始化</li><li>GeoServer 后台运行、数据持久化</li><li>服务依赖健康检查（先启动数据库）</li><li>一键启停&#x2F;重启&#x2F;查看日志</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="二、前置准备"><a href="#二、前置准备" class="headerlink" title="二、前置准备"></a>二、前置准备</h2><h3 id="1-启用-WSL2"><a href="#1-启用-WSL2" class="headerlink" title="1. 启用 WSL2"></a>1. 启用 WSL2</h3><p>以管理员打开 PowerShell：</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">wsl <span class="hljs-literal">--install</span><br>wsl <span class="hljs-literal">--set-default-version</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-安装并配置-Docker-Desktop"><a href="#2-安装并配置-Docker-Desktop" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装并配置 Docker Desktop"></a>2. 安装并配置 Docker Desktop</h3><ul><li>安装 Docker Desktop</li><li>设置 → General → 勾选 <code>Use the WSL 2 based engine</code></li><li>Resources → WSL Integration → 开启对应发行版（Ubuntu 等）</li><li>重启 Docker Desktop</li></ul><p>在 WSL 终端验证：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">docker --version<br>docker-compose --version<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="三、项目文件结构"><a href="#三、项目文件结构" class="headerlink" title="三、项目文件结构"></a>三、项目文件结构</h2><figure class="highlight nix"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nix">geoserver-deploy<span class="hljs-symbol">/</span><br>├── docker-compose.yml    <span class="hljs-comment"># 服务编排</span><br>└── geoserver-deploy.sh  <span class="hljs-comment"># 一键运维脚本</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="四、docker-compose-yml（核心配置）"><a href="#四、docker-compose-yml（核心配置）" class="headerlink" title="四、docker-compose.yml（核心配置）"></a>四、docker-compose.yml（核心配置）</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">version:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;3.8&#x27;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-attr">networks:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">geoserver-net:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">driver:</span> <span class="hljs-string">bridge</span><br><br><span class="hljs-attr">volumes:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">postgis_data:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">geoserver_data:</span><br><br><span class="hljs-attr">services:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">postgis:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">image:</span> <span class="hljs-string">kartoza/postgis:16-3.4</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">container_name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">geoserver-postgis</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">restart:</span> <span class="hljs-string">always</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">networks:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">geoserver-net</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">volumes:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">postgis_data:/var/lib/postgresql</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">environment:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">POSTGRES_USER=geoserver</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">POSTGRES_PASSWORD=GeoServer@123</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">POSTGRES_DB=gis</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">ALLOW_IP_RANGE=0.0.0.0/0</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">POSTGRES_MULTIPLE_EXTENSIONS=postgis,hstore,postgis_topology</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">ports:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;5432:5432&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">healthcheck:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">test:</span> [<span class="hljs-string">&quot;CMD-SHELL&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;pg_isready -U geoserver -d gis&quot;</span>]<br>      <span class="hljs-attr">interval:</span> <span class="hljs-string">10s</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">timeout:</span> <span class="hljs-string">5s</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">retries:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span><br><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">geoserver:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">image:</span> <span class="hljs-string">kartoza/geoserver:2.25.0</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">container_name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">geoserver-main</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">restart:</span> <span class="hljs-string">always</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">networks:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">geoserver-net</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">volumes:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">geoserver_data:/opt/geoserver/data_dir</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">environment:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">GEOSERVER_ADMIN_USER=admin</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">GEOSERVER_ADMIN_PASSWORD=GeoServer@Admin123</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">INITIAL_MEMORY=1G</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">MAXIMUM_MEMORY=2G</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">INSTALL_EXTENSIONS=true</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">STABLE_EXTENSIONS=ysld,vectortiles,printing</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">ports:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;8080:8080&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">depends_on:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">postgis:</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">condition:</span> <span class="hljs-string">service_healthy</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="五、一键运维脚本-geoserver-deploy-sh"><a href="#五、一键运维脚本-geoserver-deploy-sh" class="headerlink" title="五、一键运维脚本 geoserver-deploy.sh"></a>五、一键运维脚本 geoserver-deploy.sh</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-meta">#!/bin/bash</span><br><br>RED=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\033[0;31m&#x27;</span><br>GREEN=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\033[0;32m&#x27;</span><br>YELLOW=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\033[1;33m&#x27;</span><br>NC=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\033[0m&#x27;</span><br><br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">start</span></span>() &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;YELLOW&#125;</span>启动 GeoServer + PostGIS...<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;NC&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br>  docker-compose up -d<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;GREEN&#125;</span>启动完成！<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;NC&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;YELLOW&#125;</span>GeoServer: http://localhost:8080/geoserver<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;NC&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;账号: admin / 密码: GeoServer@Admin123&quot;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;YELLOW&#125;</span>PostGIS: localhost:5432<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;NC&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;库名: gis / 用户: geoserver / 密码: GeoServer@123<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;NC&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">stop</span></span>() &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;YELLOW&#125;</span>停止服务...<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;NC&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br>  docker-compose down<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">restart</span></span>() &#123;<br>  stop<br>  start<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">logs</span></span>() &#123;<br>  docker-compose logs -f geoserver<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">help</span></span>() &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;用法：<span class="hljs-variable">$0</span> &#123;start|stop|restart|logs|help&#125;&quot;</span><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$1</span>&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span><br>  start) start ;;<br>  stop) stop ;;<br>  restart) restart ;;<br>  logs) logs ;;<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">help</span>) <span class="hljs-built_in">help</span> ;;<br>  *) <span class="hljs-built_in">help</span> ;;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">esac</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="六、WSL-下部署步骤（与-Linux-基本一致）"><a href="#六、WSL-下部署步骤（与-Linux-基本一致）" class="headerlink" title="六、WSL 下部署步骤（与 Linux 基本一致）"></a>六、WSL 下部署步骤（与 Linux 基本一致）</h2><ol><li>进入 WSL，创建目录并放入上述两个文件</li><li>添加执行权限：<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> +x geoserver-deploy.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>启动服务：<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">./geoserver-deploy.sh start<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>访问：<ul><li>GeoServer：<code>http://localhost:8080/geoserver</code></li><li>PostGIS 可使用 DBeaver&#x2F;Navicat 连接</li></ul></li></ol><p>常用命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">./geoserver-deploy.sh start    <span class="hljs-comment"># 启动</span><br>./geoserver-deploy.sh stop     <span class="hljs-comment"># 停止</span><br>./geoserver-deploy.sh restart  <span class="hljs-comment"># 重启</span><br>./geoserver-deploy.sh logs     <span class="hljs-comment"># 实时日志</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="七、WSL-注意事项"><a href="#七、WSL-注意事项" class="headerlink" title="七、WSL 注意事项"></a>七、WSL 注意事项</h2><ol><li><strong>必须使用 WSL2</strong>，WSL1 不支持 Docker 正常运行</li><li>数据卷默认使用 Docker 卷，性能稳定、不建议挂载到 <code>/mnt/c</code></li><li>Windows 直接访问 <code>localhost</code> 即可，无需手动转发端口</li><li>若 8080&#x2F;5432 被占用，修改 <code>ports</code> 映射（如 <code>8081:8080</code>）</li><li>生产环境务必修改所有默认密码</li></ol><h2 id="八、总结"><a href="#八、总结" class="headerlink" title="八、总结"></a>八、总结</h2><ul><li><strong>简单</strong>：一条命令启动整套 GIS 环境</li><li><strong>干净</strong>：Docker 隔离，不污染系统环境</li><li><strong>稳定</strong>：健康检查 + 依赖顺序，启动无报错</li><li><strong>可迁移</strong>：复制两个文件即可在任意 Linux&#x2F;WSL 机器重建环境</li></ul><hr>]]></content>
    
    
    
