    <title>开启 Web 3D 旅程：用 Three.js 打造惊艳的个人作品集</title>
    <link href="/2026/03/02/three.js/Three.js%20Beginner&#39;s%20Tutorial/"/>
    <url>/2026/03/02/three.js/Three.js%20Beginner&#39;s%20Tutorial/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这份技术博客基于 <strong>Fireship</strong> 的经典教程：<strong>《Build a Mindblowing 3D Portfolio Website &#x2F;&#x2F; Three.js Beginner’s Tutorial》</strong>。</p><hr><h1 id="开启-Web-3D-旅程：用-Three-js-打造惊艳的个人作品集"><a href="#开启-Web-3D-旅程：用-Three-js-打造惊艳的个人作品集" class="headerlink" title="开启 Web 3D 旅程：用 Three.js 打造惊艳的个人作品集"></a>开启 Web 3D 旅程：用 Three.js 打造惊艳的个人作品集</h1><p>在现代 Web 开发中，3D 视觉效果已不再是奢侈品。借助 <strong>Three.js</strong>，我们可以通过几行代码在浏览器中构建出电影级的交互场景。本文将带你拆解 Fireship 教程中的核心逻辑，从零搭建一个动态滚动的 3D 作品集页面。</p><hr><h2 id="🛠️-环境准备：Vite-Three-js"><a href="#🛠️-环境准备：Vite-Three-js" class="headerlink" title="🛠️ 环境准备：Vite + Three.js"></a>🛠️ 环境准备：Vite + Three.js</h2><p>我们将使用 <strong>Vite</strong> 作为构建工具，它能提供极速的热更新体验。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 初始化项目</span><br>npm init vite@latest my-3d-site -- --template vanilla<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> my-3d-site<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 安装 Three.js</span><br>npm install three<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="🏗️-逻辑架构：3D-世界的“三大支柱”"><a href="#🏗️-逻辑架构：3D-世界的“三大支柱”" class="headerlink" title="🏗️ 逻辑架构：3D 世界的“三大支柱”"></a>🏗️ 逻辑架构：3D 世界的“三大支柱”</h2><p>在 Three.js 中，创建一个可视化世界就像在现实中拍摄电影，你需要：<strong>场景（Scene）</strong>、<strong>相机（Camera）和渲染器（Renderer）</strong>。</p><h3 id="1-场景与相机设置"><a href="#1-场景与相机设置" class="headerlink" title="1. 场景与相机设置"></a>1. 场景与相机设置</h3><p>场景是容器，相机是观察者的眼睛。我们通常使用 <code>PerspectiveCamera</code>（透视相机）来模拟人眼的视觉效果。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> * <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;three&#x27;</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 1. 创建场景</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> scene = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">Scene</span>();<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 2. 设置相机 (视角, 宽高比, 近剪裁面, 远剪裁面)</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> camera = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">PerspectiveCamera</span>(<span class="hljs-number">75</span>, <span class="hljs-variable language_">window</span>.<span class="hljs-property">innerWidth</span> / <span class="hljs-variable language_">window</span>.<span class="hljs-property">innerHeight</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1000</span>);<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 3. 渲染器</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> renderer = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">WebGLRenderer</span>(&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">canvas</span>: <span class="hljs-variable language_">document</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;#bg&#x27;</span>),<br>&#125;);<br><br>renderer.<span class="hljs-title function_">setPixelRatio</span>(<span class="hljs-variable language_">window</span>.<span class="hljs-property">devicePixelRatio</span>);<br>renderer.<span class="hljs-title function_">setSize</span>(<span class="hljs-variable language_">window</span>.<span class="hljs-property">innerWidth</span>, <span class="hljs-variable language_">window</span>.<span class="hljs-property">innerHeight</span>);<br>camera.<span class="hljs-property">position</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">setZ</span>(<span class="hljs-number">30</span>); <span class="hljs-comment">// 将相机向后移动</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="🎨-创造物体：几何体与材质"><a href="#🎨-创造物体：几何体与材质" class="headerlink" title="🎨 创造物体：几何体与材质"></a>🎨 创造物体：几何体与材质</h2><p>一个 3D 物体由 <strong>几何体 (Geometry)</strong> 和 <strong>材质 (Material)</strong> 组合成 <strong>网格 (Mesh)</strong>。</p><h3 id="核心代码：创建一个环面（Torus）"><a href="#核心代码：创建一个环面（Torus）" class="headerlink" title="核心代码：创建一个环面（Torus）"></a>核心代码：创建一个环面（Torus）</h3><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> geometry = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">TorusGeometry</span>(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">16</span>, <span class="hljs-number">100</span>);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> material = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">MeshStandardMaterial</span>(&#123; <span class="hljs-attr">color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0xFF6347</span> &#125;);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> torus = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">Mesh</span>(geometry, material);<br><br>scene.<span class="hljs-title function_">add</span>(torus);<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><strong>注意</strong>：这里使用了 <code>MeshStandardMaterial</code>（标准材质），这种材质对光照有反应，能产生阴影和反光。</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="💡-注入生命：光影与动画"><a href="#💡-注入生命：光影与动画" class="headerlink" title="💡 注入生命：光影与动画"></a>💡 注入生命：光影与动画</h2><h3 id="1-添加光照"><a href="#1-添加光照" class="headerlink" title="1. 添加光照"></a>1. 添加光照</h3><p>没有光，标准材质将是一片漆黑。</p><ul><li><strong>PointLight</strong>：类似灯泡，向四周发光。</li><li><strong>AmbientLight</strong>：环境光，均匀照射整个场景。</li></ul><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> pointLight = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">PointLight</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0xffffff</span>);<br>pointLight.<span class="hljs-property">position</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">set</span>(<span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">5</span>);<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> ambientLight = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">AmbientLight</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0xffffff</span>);<br>scene.<span class="hljs-title function_">add</span>(pointLight, ambientLight);<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-渲染循环（Animation-Loop）"><a href="#2-渲染循环（Animation-Loop）" class="headerlink" title="2. 渲染循环（Animation Loop）"></a>2. 渲染循环（Animation Loop）</h3><p>为了让画面动起来，我们需要每秒渲染约 60 次。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">animate</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-title function_">requestAnimationFrame</span>(animate);<br><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 让环面自转</span><br>  torus.<span class="hljs-property">rotation</span>.<span class="hljs-property">x</span> += <span class="hljs-number">0.01</span>;<br>  torus.<span class="hljs-property">rotation</span>.<span class="hljs-property">y</span> += <span class="hljs-number">0.005</span>;<br>  torus.<span class="hljs-property">rotation</span>.<span class="hljs-property">z</span> += <span class="hljs-number">0.01</span>;<br><br>  renderer.<span class="hljs-title function_">render</span>(scene, camera);<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-title function_">animate</span>();<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="🌌-场景增强：星空效果"><a href="#🌌-场景增强：星空效果" class="headerlink" title="🌌 场景增强：星空效果"></a>🌌 场景增强：星空效果</h2><p>教程中一个令人惊叹的效果是成千上万颗随机分布的星星。这通过一个简单的循环和随机函数实现：</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">addStar</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> geometry = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">SphereGeometry</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0.25</span>, <span class="hljs-number">24</span>, <span class="hljs-number">24</span>);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> material = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">MeshStandardMaterial</span>(&#123; <span class="hljs-attr">color</span>: <span class="hljs-number">0xffffff</span> &#125;);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> star = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-title class_">Mesh</span>(geometry, material);<br><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 使用 MathUtils 生成随机位置</span><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> [x, y, z] = <span class="hljs-title class_">Array</span>(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>).<span class="hljs-title function_">fill</span>().<span class="hljs-title function_">map</span>(<span class="hljs-function">() =&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">THREE</span>.<span class="hljs-property">MathUtils</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">randFloatSpread</span>(<span class="hljs-number">100</span>));<br>  <br>  star.<span class="hljs-property">position</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">set</span>(x, y, z);<br>  scene.<span class="hljs-title function_">add</span>(star);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 生成 200 颗星星</span><br><span class="hljs-title class_">Array</span>(<span class="hljs-number">200</span>).<span class="hljs-title function_">fill</span>().<span class="hljs-title function_">forEach</span>(addStar);<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="📜-核心交互：随滚动而舞动"><a href="#📜-核心交互：随滚动而舞动" class="headerlink" title="📜 核心交互：随滚动而舞动"></a>📜 核心交互：随滚动而舞动</h2><p>本教程的灵魂在于：<strong>3D 场景随 HTML 页面的滚动而移动</strong>。</p><h3 id="关键代码：移动相机逻辑"><a href="#关键代码：移动相机逻辑" class="headerlink" title="关键代码：移动相机逻辑"></a>关键代码：移动相机逻辑</h3><p>我们需要监听浏览器的滚动事件，并根据 <code>getBoundingClientRect().top</code> 计算偏移量。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">moveCamera</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> t = <span class="hljs-variable language_">document</span>.<span class="hljs-property">body</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">getBoundingClientRect</span>().<span class="hljs-property">top</span>;<br><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 旋转物体</span><br>  moon.<span class="hljs-property">rotation</span>.<span class="hljs-property">x</span> += <span class="hljs-number">0.05</span>;<br>  moon.<span class="hljs-property">rotation</span>.<span class="hljs-property">y</span> += <span class="hljs-number">0.075</span>;<br>  moon.<span class="hljs-property">rotation</span>.<span class="hljs-property">z</span> += <span class="hljs-number">0.05</span>;<br><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 移动相机位置 (向下滚动时 t 为负值)</span><br>  camera.<span class="hljs-property">position</span>.<span class="hljs-property">z</span> = t * -<span class="hljs-number">0.01</span>;<br>  camera.<span class="hljs-property">position</span>.<span class="hljs-property">x</span> = t * -<span class="hljs-number">0.0002</span>;<br>  camera.<span class="hljs-property">rotation</span>.<span class="hljs-property">y</span> = t * -<span class="hljs-number">0.0002</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-variable language_">document</span>.<span class="hljs-property">body</span>.<span class="hljs-property">onscroll</span> = moveCamera;<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="🚀-总结与进阶"><a href="#🚀-总结与进阶" class="headerlink" title="🚀 总结与进阶"></a>🚀 总结与进阶</h2><p>Three.js 的核心流程：</p><ol><li><strong>初始化环境</strong>（三大件）。</li><li><strong>创建资产</strong>（几何体 + 贴图）。</li><li><strong>布局空间</strong>（光照 + 随机分布）。</li><li><strong>联动交互</strong>（将 DOM 滚动与 3D 变换绑定）。</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th>核心组件</th><th>功能描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>TextureLoader</strong></td><td>用于给物体穿上“外衣”（如月球表面纹理）</td></tr><tr><td><strong>OrbitControls</strong></td><td>调试利器，允许鼠标拖拽缩放查看场景</td></tr><tr><td><strong>MathUtils</strong></td><td>快速处理 3D 空间内的随机数学运算</td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>建议下一步尝试：</strong> </p><ul><li>添加 <strong>GSAP</strong> 实现更平滑的补间动画。</li><li>学习 <strong>Shaders (GLSL)</strong> 编写自定义的视觉效果。</li></ul><hr>]]></content>
    
    
